casebody.data:
Burl Anderson HOWELL, petitioner,
v.
Robert B. YOUNG, Judge, Superior Court of Delaware, Kent County, et al. No. 13-5626. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 15, 2013.

Case below, 530 Fed.Appx. ----.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
